  "details": "A vulnerability was identified in D-Link DIR-605L 2.13B01. Impacted is the function formSetLog of the file /goform/formSetLog of the component POST Request Handler. The manipulation of the argument curTime leads to buffer overflow. The attack is possible to be carried out remotely. The exploit is publicly available and might be used. This vulnerability only affects products that are no longer supported by the maintainer.",
